## OpenCollective Personal Token
## Production: generate at https://opencollective.com/dashboard/{slug}/for-developers/personal-tokens/
## Staging (ORIGIN mode): generate at https://staging.opencollective.com/dashboard/{slug}/for-developers/personal-tokens/
OCAPIKEY="xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx"
OCSLUG="yyyyyyyyyy"
## OC_API is optional — auto-detected from ~/.ipfs/swarm.key:
##   All-zeros swarm key (ORIGIN mode) → https://api-staging.opencollective.com/graphql/v2
##   Real swarm key (production)       → https://api.opencollective.com/graphql/v2
## Uncomment to override auto-detection:
# OC_API="https://api.opencollective.com/graphql/v2"
